---
import wifiIcon from '../../assets/images/wifiIcon.svg';
---
<section class="w-full flex 2xl:px-52 lg: px-8 md:px-20 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 p-4 bg-gray-100">
    <h1 class="text-xl md:text-4xl text-grisT font-bold">Triaso® Control System</h1>
    <p class="text-base md:text-xl text-grisT font-bold text-center">Offering a practical and efficient 
        way to manage industrial equipment operations. With advanced monitoring and
         automation, it simplifies the control of key processes like temperature, 
         material dosing, and production rates. Built to adapt to different setups,
         it ensures reliable performance while prioritizing safety and ease of use.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
            <button class="text-xs md:text-base tab-button py-2 md:px-4 font-bold focus:outline-none"
            data-tab="tab1" aria-selected="true">
                Process Control, Automation, and Safety
            </button>
            <button class="tab-button py-2 md:px-4 font-bold text-xs md:text-base focus:outline-none"
            data-tab="tab2" aria-selected="false">
                Control Cabin
            </button>
            <button class="tab-button py-2 px-4 font-bold text-xs md:text-base focus:outline-none"
            data-tab="tab3" aria-selected="false">
                Adaptability and Configuration
            </button>
            <button class="tab-button py-2 px-4 font-bold text-xs md:text-base focus:outline-none"
            data-tab="tab4" aria-selected="false">
                Equipment, Connectivity, and Maintenance
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="py-4">
            <!-- First Section -->
        <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-4 tab-content text-xs md:text-base" data-tab-content="tab1">
            <div class="col-span-2 flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold">
                    <h1 class="text-black">Visualization and control of materials consumption (current and cumulative).</h1>
                    <p class="text-grisT font-normal">Enables real-time monitoring of material usage, while tracking total 
                        consumption over time for accurate records and optimized production.</p>
                    <ul class="pl-4 mt-2 font-normal text-grisT">
                        <li class="list-disc">Asphalt</li>
                        <li class="list-disc">Aggregates</li>
                        <li class="list-disc">Fuel Consumption</li>
                        <li class="list-disc">Water Usage</li>
                        <li class="list-disc">Recycled Asphalt Pavement (RAP)</li>
                        <li class="list-disc">Additives</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center mt-4">
                    <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold h-full text-grisT">
                        <h1>Customizable production management with storage for 
                            thousands of recipes.</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold text-grisT ml-4 h-full">
                        <h1>
                            Real-time monitoring of temperatures (mix, aggregates, exhaust gases).
                        </h1>
                        <p class="font-light">
                          Continuously tracks key temperatures to ensure optimal production 
                          conditions and prevent issues like overheating or inefficiency  
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold text-grisT mt-4 h-full">
                    <h1 class="">Supervision and control of material dosing with 
                        configurable percentages.
                    </h1>
                    <p class="font-normal">
                        Allows precise adjustment of the proportions of materials like asphalt and aggregates, 
                        ensuring consistency and meeting mix specifications.
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold text-grisT h-full">
                    <h1 class="text-black text-base md:text-xl mb-2">
                        Stop System
                    </h1>
                    <h2 class="text-grisT">
                        Sequential start and stop system to prevent operational errors.
                        <br><br>Emergency stop system with maintenance lockout.
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-normal text-grisT mt-4 h-full">
                    <p>Visual and audible alarms that notify operators of high temperatures 
                        or critical system issues, ensuring timely responses and enhanced safety.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold text-grisT mt-4 h-full">
                    <h1>Automatic equipment operation with spill and overflow prevention</h1>
                    <br>
                    <p class="font-light">Ensures precise control during the operation of tanks and other systems, 
                        automatically stopping processes to prevent spills, overflows, or material waste, 
                        enhancing safety and efficiency.</p>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>
        <!-- Second Section -->
         <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-4 tab-content text-xs md:text-base text-grisT" data-tab-content="tab2">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold w-full">
                    <h1>Walls and roof made of 16-gauge sheet metal with insulated panels.</h1>
                    <br>
                    <p class="font-normal text-left leading-relaxed tracking-wide max-w-prose">Provides durability and thermal insulation, ensuring structural strength
                        while maintaining a controlled interior environment.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-semibold w-full">
                    <h1>Internal structure of 2” and 1.5” PTR.</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-semibold w-full">
                    <h1>Equipped with a 1.5-ton air conditioning unit for a comfortable workspace.</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-semibold w-full">
                    <h1>Panoramic windows for enhanced visibility.</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start">
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-semibold w-full">
                    <h1>Galvanized fasteners for durability and easy maintenance.</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-semibold w-full">
                    <h1>Automotive-grade electrostatic paint for long-lasting corrosion resistance.</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start">
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-semibold w-full">
                    <h1>Built with reinforced materials for heavy-duty use.</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-semibold w-full">
                    <h1 class="">Standard 110V electrical installation with interior lighting.</h1>
                    <br>
                    <p class="font-normal text-left leading-relaxed tracking-wide max-w-prose">Offers reliable power for equipment and provides well-lit
                         working conditions inside the unit.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
         </div>
         <!-- Third Section -->
          <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-4 tab-content text-xs md:text-base" data-tab-content="tab3">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-semibold w-full">
                    <h1>Flexible Installation</h1>
                    <br>
                    <p class="font-normal text-grisT">
                        Can be positioned up to 8 meters from the equipment for optimal site integration.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 w-full font-bold">
                    <h1 class="text-lg md:text-2xl">Versatile Setup</h1>
                    <p class="text-grisT">
                        Works seamlessly in a dedicated control cabin or under a protective roof.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 font-bold w-full">
                    <h1 class="text-lg md:text-2xl">Quick Adjustments</h1>
                    <p class="text-grisT">
                        Allows rapid changes to recipes or control settings to match project requirements.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start">
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold w-full">
                    <h1 class="text-base md:text-xl">Advanced Automation Options</h1>
                    <br>
                    <p class="text-grisT font-normal">
                        Supports weight-based control for precise material 
                        dosing or time-based control for process efficiency.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold w-full">
                    <h1 class="text-base md:text-xl">User-Friendly Interface</h1>
                    <br>
                    <p class="font-normal text-grisT">
                        Simplifies configuration adjustments for operators with minimal downtime.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start">
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold w-full">
                    <h1 class="text-base md:text-xl">Scalable Configuration</h1>
                    <br>
                    <p class="font-normal text-grisT">
                        Easily adapts to upgrades or additional equipment integration.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <!-- Fourth Section -->
         <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-4 tab-content text-xs md:text-base" data-tab-content="tab4">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start">
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold w-full">
                    <h1>Industrial-grade components, with 95% from brands like Siemens™.</h1>
                    <br>
                    <p class="font-normal text-grisT">
                        Ensures high reliability and durability, using trusted and globally recognized 
                        brands for key elements of the system. These components are designed to perform 
                        in demanding industrial environments, offering precision, longevity, 
                        and ease of maintenance.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold w-full text-grisT">
                    <h1>12” touchscreen console with optional wireless mouse control.</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold w-full text-grisT">
                    <h1>Baghouse cleaning system for efficient operation.</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start col-span-2">
                <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold w-full">
                    <h1 class="text-base md:text-xl">Advanced sensors, including guided wave radar for level monitoring</h1>
                    <div class="font-normal text-grisT grid grid-cols-2 justify-around gap-20 pt-3">
                        <p class="text-justify">Provide precise measurements of materials like asphalt or aggregates,
                             unaffected by dust or temperature. They track levels to prevent overflows or shortages, 
                             ensuring efficient inventory management and seamless operation.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="mr-4">
                            <li class="list-disc">Asphalt Tanks</li>
                            <li class="list-disc">Aggregate Silos</li>
                            <li class="list-disc">Water Tanks</li>
                            <li class="list-disc">Bins</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-4">
                    <div class="shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 font-bold w-full h-fit text-grisT">
                        <img src={wifiIcon.src} alt="" class="w-10 md:w-12">
                        <h1>Remote access via the internet for diagnostics and technical support.</h1>
                        <p class="font-normal text-justify max-w-prose [hyphens:auto] [text-wrap:balance]">Enables real-time monitoring, troubleshooting, and system adjustments 
                            from anywhere. This reduces downtime, allows remote issue resolution,
                             and ensures efficient operation without needing on-site intervention.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 p-6 font-bold w-full text-grisT">
                        <div class="w-full">
                            <h2 class="">Digital</h2>
                            <h1 class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-black">Operation Log</h1>
                            <h2 class="text-xs md:text-sm">with export and ticket printing options.</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-full">
                            <h2 class="">Real-time</h2>
                            <h1 class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-black">Communication Via SMS</h1>
                            <h2 class="">about operational status.</h2>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                        <div class="w-full font-bold text-grisT p-4">
                            <h2 class="">Guided</h2>
                            <h1 class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-black">Thermocouple Calibration</h1>
                            <h2 class="">for accurate adjustments.</h2>
                        </div>
                    
                    
                        <div class="w-full font-bold text-grisT p-4">
                            <h2 class="">On-screen</h2>
                            <h1 class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-black">Maintenance Log</h1>
                            <h2 class="">with operational hour indicators.</h2>
                        </div>
                    

                </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>    
    </div>
</section>
<style is:global>
  /* Estilos para los tabs activos */
  .tab-button[aria-selected="true"] {
    color: var(--azul-bg1);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--azul-bg1);
  }
  
  .tab-button[aria-selected="false"] {
    color: var(--gris-titulos);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gris-titulos);
  }
  
  .tab-button:hover:not([aria-selected="true"]) {
    color: var(--azul-bg1);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--azul-bg1);
  }
  
</style>
<script is:inline>
  // Mover la lógica fuera del DOMContentLoaded para ejecutarse inmediatamente
  (function initTabs() {
    const tabButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
    
    // Ocultar todos los contenidos excepto el primero
    document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content').forEach((content, index) => {
      content.classList.toggle('hidden', index !== 0);
    });
    
    // Configurar los listeners
    tabButtons.forEach(button => {
      button.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const tabId = button.getAttribute('data-tab');
        
        tabButtons.forEach(btn => {
          btn.setAttribute('aria-selected', 'false');
        });
        
        button.setAttribute('aria-selected', 'true');
        
        document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content').forEach(content => {
          content.classList.add('hidden');
        });
        
        document.querySelector(`.tab-content[data-tab-content="${tabId}"]`).classList.remove('hidden');
      });
    });
  })();
</script>